   "## Concept: MCP integration\n",
   "\n",
   "Model Context Protocol extends tools via external servers.\n",
   "\n",
   "**Harness Agent** implements this subsystem in ``mcp/client.py``. External harnesses differ in scale (tool count, platforms) but share the same architectural slot.\n",
   "\n",
   "| Concern | Harness Agent | Hermes (reference) | OpenClaw (reference) |\n",
   "|---------|---------------|--------------------|----------------------|\n",
   "| This chapter | ``mcp/client.py`` | see architecture docs | workspace/gateway docs |\n",
   "| Entry point | `AIAgent` or CLI | `run_agent.py` / gateway | gateway + workspace |\n"
  ]
 },
 {
  "cell_type": "markdown",
  "metadata": {},
  "source": [
   "## How it works\n",
   "\n",
   "`MCPIntegration.connect_stdio_sync` registers `mcp_*` tools.\n",
   "\n",
   "```mermaid\n",
   "flowchart LR\n",
   "  U[User or scheduler] --> A[AIAgent]\n",
   "  A --> M[MCP integration]\n",
   "```\n",
